overview: Alice has recently begun seeing Noah - a dark, handsome man with a vague past, and is introduced to his older sister Lucy, who shares the same dark beauty as her brother. Along with her friends Cassia, and the twins Jack and Daniel, Alice agrees to try out a new party drug called Wonderland on a night out. She soon finds however that Wonderland is indeed a fantastical trip - but the effects are deadly.
title: Alice
